      "text": "DDR-IF-high tumors were characterized by a distinct biological profile, including (i) transcriptional exhaustion of the cGAS-STING innate immune pathway (p < 0.001), (ii) significantly reduced CD8+ T cell infiltration (2.3-fold fewer, p = 0.004), and (iii) a superior pooled objective response rate to PARP-ICB combinations (42% vs 18%; risk ratio 2.3, 95% CI 1.3-4.2; p = 0.003).",
