      "text_span_id": "methods_3",
      "text": "The final DDR-IF score was defined using standardized coefficients: DDR-IF = 0.4 \u00d7 (HRD score) + 0.35 \u00d7 log10(TMB + 1) + 0.25 \u00d7 (STING activation score), where all predictors were z-score normalized prior to model fitting.",
      "confidence": 0.95,
      "extraction_method": "llm",
      "study_type": "biomarker development",
